    "body": "Hi @nklmilojevic,\r\n\r\nI hadn't worked on this since, but now that I have a bit of time to spare, I would like to get this to work properly and merged if possible. There are three aspects to this feature:\r\n- starship cli support\r\n- shell init scripts support\r\n- modules support \r\n\r\nAs a first step, I have created a PR that adds this functionality only for the `custom command` module and for `zsh` shell. For now, no fancy features (e.g. alias expansion) and very little support. If maintainers think this feature should be merged, I (or anyone who wants) will then build upon that to bring support for fish and powershell, and make the configuration flag available for eventually every single module.\r\n\r\nBut before spending too much time on this, I would like to have some feedback from the maintainers on whether or not this feature might ever make it into starship.",
